#Superplastic I know you guys want to build cool stuff and have fun in this space. But know that people are literally throwing MILLIONS of dollars at you. There's a fine line between being "Janky" (on brand) and being professional at what you do. (9/10)

7) You constantly switched up your URLs, your rules of the game, giving scammers an opportunity to cash in. (5/10)

5) Your second "Anti-bot" raffles is just as bad. People who joined ON THE DOT were not able to submit their addresses. (4/10)

2) When pills were holding at a floor price well above 0.4ETH, you released sales of an overwhelming amount of pills at 0.24ETH, undercutting the FP of your loyal holders.

1) You changed pills conversion from 4:1 to 3:1, hurting loyal fans who joined in early. (2/10)
